== Personal life ==
Fincher and his wife, Lynn, have three children.  They live in Frog Jump, an unincorporated community just outside [[Halls, Tennessee|Halls]].  He is a lifetime member of Archer's Chapel United Methodist Church<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.archerschapel.com |title=Archer's Chapel |publisher=Archerschapel.com |date= |accessdate=2010-11-02}}</ref>

Stephen has raised money for the [[Methodist Church]], [[Little League Baseball|Dixie Youth Baseball]], [[NOAH]]{{dn|date=May 2013}}, and [[Relay for Life]]. He is a lifetime member of the [[National Rifle Association|NRA]].

